\f1\b\fs26 \ulnone Reputation Feature
\f0\b0 \
Similarly to the badge system, as you start posting, voting, winning in competitions, etc, you will notice your reputation increase. The more active you are on BuzzZap, the higher your reputation will be. On a user\'92s home page, you can see in the top right the community leader board. This is based and judged purely on reputation. 
