\cf5 \ulnone Inbox page\

\fs26 \cf0 \
Your inbox is simply a private messaging service that allows you to contact any other user on the site, even if they are not part of your community. \

\fs40 \cf5 \

\f1\b\fs26 \cf0 Sending a new message
\f0\b0 \
To send a new message, go to your inbox, and click \'93start new message\'94 on the top left of the page. The message form will appear. Then, enter a message subject and then who you want to send your message to. If you want to send your message to multiple users then enter each of their usernames separated by commas, for example: \'93username1, username2, group123, etc\'94. You can also enter a group name and the message will be received by everyone in that group. 
