\fs40 \cf5 I Wonder Board\

\fs26 \cf0 \

\f1\b Purpose
\f0\b0 \
\
The I Wonder board is separate to the rest of the site. It is global. Any user from any community sees the same I Wonder board with the same content. It is essentially a virtual sticky board and any user can add a new sticky note which is a mini discussion. Every discussion question must start with \'93I Wonder\'85\'94.\
\

\f1\b Adding a question
\f0\b0 \
\
To add a new sticky note/question, click \'93Add sticky note\'94, enter your question, then click anywhere on the page to save it. It will require approval if your reputation is under 20.
